ionship#Title history|1 time]]) \u2013 with Jeff Hardy<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pwtorch.com/site/2017/01/30/128-mcw-pro-wrestling-broken-anniversary-broken-hardys-vs-ecktourage-king-maxel-vs-kevin-eck-big-sean-studd-vs-prolix-belina-vs-brittany-blake/|title=1/28 MCW Pro Wrestling \u2013 Broken Anniversary: The \"Broken\" Hardys vs. The Ecktourage, King Maxel vs. Kevin Eck, \"Big\" Sean Studd vs. Prolix, Belina vs. Brittany Blake|accessdate=January 30, 2017|work=Pro Wrestling Torch|date=January 30, 2017}}</ref>\n** [[Extreme Rising#Championship|Extreme Rising World Championship]] ([[Extreme Rising World Championship#Title history|1 time]]){{Efn|Hardy's reign was not recognized by Extreme Rising.<ref name=\"odd\">{{cite web|url=http://www.pwinsider.com/article/87020/odd-situation-involving-extreme-rising-championship.html?p=1|title=Odd Situation Involving Extreme Rising Championship|last=Johnson|first=Mike|date=July 19, 2014|accessdate=November 30, 2017|work=PWInsider.com }}</ref>}}\n* '''National Championship Wrestling'''\n** NCW Heavyweight Championship (1 time)<ref name=\"OWOW\"/>\n** NCW Light Heavyweight Championship (1 time)<ref name=\"OWOW\"/>\n* '''New Dimension Wrestling'''\n** NDW Light Heavyweight Championship (1 time)<ref name=\"OWOW\"/>\n** NDW Tag Team Championship (1 time){{Efn|The title was vacated in 1999 due to [[The Hardy Boyz]] signing contracts with the WWF.}} \u2013 with Jeff Hardy<ref>{{cite web|url=http://users.domaindlx.com/ndwwrestling/history.htm|title=New Dimension Wrestling Title History|accessdate=October 11, 2010|publisher=New Dimension Wrestling|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710143437/http://users.domaindlx.com/ndwwrestling/history.htm|archivedate=July 10, 2011}}</ref>\n* '''New England Wrestling Alliance'''\n** NEWA Heavyweight Championship (1 time)<ref name=\"OWOW\"/>\n** NEWA Hall of Fame (class of 2012)\n* '''New Frontier Wrestling Association'''\n** NFWA Heavyweight Championship (1 time)<ref name=\"OWOW\"/><ref name=\"Slam\"/>\n** NFWA Tag Team Championship (1 time) \u2013 with [[Jason Arhndt|Venom]]<ref name=\"OWOW\"/>\n* '''[[National Wrestling Alliance|NWA 2000]]'''\n** NWA 2000 Tag Team Championship (1 time) \u2013 with Jeff Hardy<ref name=\"OWOW\">{{cite web|url=http://www.onlineworldofwrestling.com/profiles/m/matt-hardy.html|title=Matt Hardy Profile|accessdate=March 21, 2008|publisher=Online World of Wrestling}}</ref><ref name=F4WMarch7>{{cite web | url=https://www.f4wonline.com/other-wrestling/daily-pro-wrestling-history-0307-bruno-sammartino-vs-giant-baba-305926 | title=Daily Pro Wrestling history (03/07): Bruno Sammartino vs. Giant Baba | work=[[Wrestling Observer Newsletter]] | first=Brian | last=Hoops | date=March 7, 2020 | accessdate=March 8, 2020}}</ref>\n*'''[[OMEGA Championship Wrestling]]'''\n** [[OMEGA Heavyweight Championship]] ([[OMEGA Heavyweight Championship#Title history|2 times]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cagematch.de/?id=5&nr=715|title=Organization Of Modern Extreme Grappling Arts \u2013 OMEGA Heavyweight Championship|accessdate=March 21, 2008|publisher=Cagematch.de|language=German}}</ref>\n**[[OMEGA Tag Team Championship]] ([[OMEGA Tag Team Championship#Title history|2 times]]) \u2013 with Jeff Hardy<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cagematch.de/?id=5&nr=714|title=OMEGA Tag Team Championship|accessdate=March 21, 2008|publisher=Cagematch.de|language=German}}</ref>\n* '''Pro Wrestling South'''\n** PWS Heavyweight Championship (1 time)\n* '''''[[Pro Wrestling Illustrated]]'''''\n** [[PWI Comeback of the Year|Comeback of the Year]] (2017) <small>with Jeff Hardy</small><ref name=\"PWI Awards\">{{cite web|url=http://www.pwi-online.com/pages/PWIawards.html|title=PWI Awards|work=[[Pro Wrestling Illustrated]]|publisher=[[Kappa Publishing Group]]|accessdate=June 7, 2018}}</ref>\n** [[PWI Feud of the Year|Feud of the Year]] (2005) <small>vs. [[Edge (wrestler)|Edge]] and [[Lita (wrestler)|Lita]]</small><ref name=\"PWI Awards\"/>\n** [[PWI Matc