ist of ECW World Heavyweight Champions|1 time]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/superstars/matt-hardy |title=Matt Hardy |publisher=WWE.com |date= |accessdate=January 20, 2016}}</ref>\n** [[WCW World Tag Team Championship|WCW Tag Team Championship]] ([[List of WCW World Tag Team Champions|1 time]]) \u2013 with Jeff Hardy<ref name=\"wwe\" />\n** [[WWE Cruiserweight Championship (1991\u20132007)|WWE Cruiserweight Championship]] ([[List of WWE Cruiserweight Champions (1991\u20132007)|1 time]])<ref name=\"Hardy's first Cruiserweight Championship reign\" />\n** [[WWE Raw Tag Team Championship|WWE (Raw) Tag Team Championship]] ([[List of WWE Raw Tag Team Champions|3 times]])<ref name=\"wwetagtitlehistory\" /> \u2013 with [[Montel Vontavious Porter]] (1), Jeff Hardy (1) and [[Bray Wyatt]] (1)\n** [[WWE SmackDown Tag Team Championship]] ([[List of WWE SmackDown Tag Team Champions|1 time]]) \u2013 with Jeff Hardy\n** [[WWE United States Championship]] ([[List of WWE United States Champions|1 time]])<ref name=\"UStitle\" />\n** [[WWE European Championship|WWF European Championship]] ([[List of WWE European Champions|1 time]])<ref name=\"WWE euro\" />\n** [[WWE Hardcore Championship|WWF Hardcore Championship]] ([[List of WWE Hardcore Champions|1 time]])<ref name=\"WWE hardcore\">{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/classics/titlehistory/hard/|title=History of the Hardcore Championship|accessdate=March 21, 2008|publisher=[[World Wrestling Entertainment]]}}</ref>\n** [[World Tag Team Championship (WWE)|WWF/World Tag Team Championship]] ([[List of World Tag Team Champions (WWE)|6 times]]) \u2013 with Jeff Hardy<ref name=\"tag team titles\">{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/classics/titlehistory/worldtagteam/|title=History of the World Tag Team Championship|accessdate=March 21, 2008|publisher=[[World Wrestling Entertainment]]}}</ref>\n** [[Bragging Rights (2009)|Bragging Rights Trophy (2009)]] \u2013 with [[WWE SmackDown|Team SmackDown]] {{small|([[Chris Jericho]], [[Kane (wrestler)|Kane]], [[R-Truth]], [[Dave Finlay|Finlay]], [[David Hart Smith]] and [[Tyson Kidd]])}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wwe.com/shows/wwebraggingrights/wwebraggingrightshistory/2009/matches/12210846/results/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101012233242/http://www.wwe.com/shows/wwebraggingrights/wwebraggingrightshistory/2009/matches/12210846/results/|title=SmackDown curses Raw|last=Passero|first=Mitch|publisher=[[World Wrestling Entertainment]]|date=October 25, 2009|archivedate=October 12, 2010|accessdate=October 25, 2009}}</ref>\n** [[Andr\u00e9 the Giant Memorial Trophy]] ([[WrestleMania 34|2018]])\n** [[Terri Runnels|Terri Invitational Tournament (1999)]]<ref name=\"NoMercy99\"/> \u2013 with Jeff Hardy\n* '''WrestleCade'''\n** WrestleCade Championship (2 times)\n* '''''[[Wrestling Observer Newsletter]]'''''\n** [[List of Wrestling Observer Newsletter awards#Best Gimmick|Best Gimmick]] (2002, 2016)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.WrestlingData.com/index.php?befehl=observer&award=34|title=Observer: Best Gimmick Of The Year|accessdate=March 21, 2008|work=Wrestling Observer Newsletter|publisher=WrestlingData}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last = Meltzer | first = Dave | authorlink = Dave Meltzer | date = March 6, 2017 | title = March 6, 2017 Wrestling Observer Newsletter: 2016 Awards issue, talent departing TNA, more | journal = [[Wrestling Observer Newsletter]] | location = [[Campbell, California]] | issn = 1083-9593 | page=26}}</ref>\n** [[List of Wrestling Observer Newsletter awards#Worst Feud of the Year|Worst Feud of the Year]] (2004) <small>with Lita vs. [[Kane (wrestler)|Kane]]</small><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.WrestlingData.com/index.php?befehl=observer&award=30|title=Observer: Worst Feud Of The Year|accessdate=March 21, 2008|publisher=WrestlingData|work=Wrestling Observer Newsletter}}</ref>\n* '''Wrestling Superstar'''\n** Wrestling Superstar Tag Team Championship (1 time) \u2013 with Jeff Hardy<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cagematch.net/?id=5&nr=2928&page=5&reign=3|title=Title Reigns \u00ab Wrestling Superstar Tag Team Championship \u00ab Titles Database \u00ab CAGEMATCH - The Internet Wrestling Database|first=Philip|last=Kreikenbohm}}</ref>\n\n== ''Luchas de Apuestas'' record ==\n{{see also|Lucha libre#Luchas de Apuestas|l1=Luchas de Apuestas}}\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%;text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! width=20%|Winner (wager)\n! width=20%|Loser (wager)\n! width=15%|Location\n! width=10%|Event\n! width=10%|Date\n! width=25% class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n|-\n|Matt Hardy (hair)|| Billy Blade (hair) || [[Santa Maria, California]] || ''Terror Rising'' || {{dts|2012|10|27}} || This was a ladder match.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vendettaprowrestling.com/main/results/2012-results/terror-rising-2012/|accessdate=January 8, 2016|title=Terror Rising 2012| publisher=Vendetta Pro Wrestling}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Notes ==\n{{notelist}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== Sources ==\n* {{cite book|title=The Hardy Boyz: Exist 2 Inspire|isbn=978-0-06-052154-7|last=Hardy|first=Jeff|author2=Hardy, Matt |author3=Krugman, Michael |publisher=HarperCollins|year=2003}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0FCO/is_2_5/ai_104609871/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040926055332/http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0FCO/is_2_5/ai_104609871|url-status=dead|archive-date=September 26, 2004|title=Interview: Matt Hardy|last=Yandek|first=Chris|publisher=Wrestling Digest|accessdate=June 4, 2007|date=August 2003}} \n* {{cite web|url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0FCO/is_4_3/ai_80302525/ |title=Matt and Jeff Hardy \u2013 Interview |last=Varsallone |first=Jim |publisher=Wrestling Digest |accessdate=June 4, 2007 |date=December 2001}}{{dead link|date=June 2016}}{{cbignore}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category}}\n* {{web archive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170724032047/http://matthardybrand.com/|date=July 24, 2017|title=Matt Hardy Brand}}\n* {{web archive|url=https://